		<span id="title-175885073" class="story-title"> <a   href="//ask.slashdot.org/story/25/01/12/0319219/ask-slashdot-whats-the-best-way-to-transfer-legacy-php-code-to-a-modern-framework">Ask Slashdot:  What's the Best Way to Transfer Legacy PHP Code to a Modern Framework?</a></span>

		
		
